parcel.description:
#Decentricity Tower, by @decentricity

##I am a refugee from Second Life! 

I created the PicoVista Museum of Computing in 2013, and it's still standing -- go see it in the Metaverse listing [here](https://www.metabizlist.com/directory/8480093/PicoVista_Museum_of_Computing.html).
I no longer have access to it so after years of making stuff there I thought I'd rather move to a platform where you actually own land instead of renting it from a large company.

# Controls
| Action       |  Key    |
| ----------- |:---------:|
| Walk forwards         | W      |
| Walk left        | A      |
| Walk backwards         | S      |
| Walk right         | D      |
| Fly          | F  |
| 3rd-person view toggle          | C       |
| Chat Box          | Enter  |
